                                <lb n="2r3=6" break="no"/><unclear>lava</unclear>to ’numatāc<unclear>ā</unclear>rālaṁkṛtasya satya-pratijñasya Aneka-go-<unclear>hiraṇya-bhū</unclear>my-ādi
                                <pb n="2v" break="no"/>
