                        vacanena karmma-<unclear>rāṣṭre</unclear> A<unclear>dhi</unclear>kṛtāḥ Āyuktakāḥ
                        <pb n="3r"/>
                        <lb n="3r1=10"/>Oṁgoḍu-grāmaś ca vaktavyāḥ        
                    </p>
                    
                    <p>
                        Asmai kāśyapāya dvi-vedāya ṣaḍ-aṅga
                        <lb n="3r2=11" break="no"/>-pāragāya gola<unclear>śar</unclear>mmaṇe Eṣaḥ oṁgoḍu-grāmaḥ sā<choice><orig>t</orig><reg>tt</reg></choice>vikena
                        <lb n="3r3=12"/>dānena deva-bhoga-hala-varjjaḥ brahmadeyīkṛtya Aṣṭā-daśa-vidha-pari
                        <pb n="3v" break="no"/>
