                        <lb n="3v2=14" break="no"/>m atikrāmeT tad-anurūpaṁ daṇ<unclear>ḍa</unclear>m arhati        
                    </p>
                    
                    <p>
                        vijaya-saṁvatsare traya
                        <lb n="3v3=15" break="no"/>str<unclear>i</unclear>ṁśe <num value="33"><g type="numeral">30</g> 3</num> hemanta-pakṣe t<unclear>ṛ</unclear>tīye 3 trayodaśy<unclear>āṁ</unclear> likhitam idaṁ śāsanaṁ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
                        
                    </p>
                    
                    <p>
                        <pb n="4r"/>
